::    With everyone's festival tolerance finally hitting exhaustion point, it's that

::
::    Celebrating all that is super fresh & forward thinking, Clubbers Guide to 2010
::    is once again a mammoth 3CD set, mixed by our sexiest ever bunch of DJs:

::    AXWELL
::
::    Our three mixing masterminds deliver the ultimate blend of the newest tracks to
::    keep MoS fans ahead of the curve. With featuring artists including Dizzee
::    Rascal, Miami Horror, Muse (yep Better believe it), Chuckie, Claude Vonstroke,
::    Florence  The Machine, Crookers feat. Kelis, Sharam feat. Kid Cudi, Green
::    Velvet feat. Kid Sister, Fake Blood, Major Lazer, The Bloody Beetroots, Miike
::    Snow, La Roux, Bag Raiders, john Dahlback and so, so much more - 63 tracks of
::    pure, unsullied electronic joy
::
::    Clubbers Guide to 2010 offers the ultimate journey for the forward looking
::    clubber and is the must have album to kick off the New Year
